    Italicize, please.
    Iterated, please.
    Iterate, please.

{,{,gotta have{ ,\, again\, }}more }cowbell!
    cowbell!
    more cowbell!
    gotta have more cowbell!
    gotta have\, again\, more cowbell!

{}} some {\\{edge,edgy} }{ cases, here\\\}
    {}} some {\\edge }{ cases, here\\\}
    {}} some {\\edgy }{ cases, here\\\}

a{b{1,2}c
    a{b1c
    a{b2c

a{1,2}b}c
    a1b}c
    a2b}c

